# 🇳🇬 Nigeria Legal Case Summarizer

**Nigeria Legal Case Summarizer** is a Streamlit-powered web application that helps legal professionals, researchers, and students quickly summarize Nigerian legal case texts.  
Simply paste the full text of a case, and the app will generate a concise summary, saving you time and improving case analysis efficiency.

🔗 **Live Demo:** [Click here to try it on Hugging Face](https://huggingface.co/spaces/LawTechQueen/nigeria-legal-case-summarizer)
---

## 🚀 Features
- **Fast summarization** – Get clear, concise summaries in seconds.
- **User-friendly interface** – Simple text area for input, instant results.
- **Nigerian legal focus** – Tailored for Nigerian case law formatting and style.
- **Web-based** – No installation required; runs on Hugging Face Spaces.

---

